name: Museum of the Mountain Man
address: Museum of the Mountain Man, Pinedale WY, 82941
info: This is a drive thru clinic for PFIZER vaccine only!
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Fremont County Public Health-Riverton
vaccines: Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine, Moderna COVID-19 Vaccine, Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 Vaccine
info: Please wear short sleeved shirts and expect to be observed for 15 minutes after your injection. If you have any anaphylactic allergies requiring use of an epi-pen in the past we will be unable to give you a vaccine, you will need to get your vaccine in a clinic or hospital. If you have any questions please call our office at 856-6979, Thank You!
special: If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
